    "methodology": "SCB Structure of Earnings Survey covers all employees in enterprises with 10+ employees. SSYK 2012 (Swedish Standard Classification of Occupations, aligns with ISCO-08). Values converted from SEK to EUR at 2022 average rate (1 EUR = 10.90 SEK) and stored as EUR equivalents for cross-country comparison.",
    "coverage": "Sweden national. Stockholm derived from SCB regional data for Stockholms län (~12% above national median for comparable roles).",
    "limitations": "EUR values are converted from SEK at 2022 average rate. Actual CHF/EUR conversion may vary. SSYK codes map to broad groups. Seniority inferred from published P25/P75 tables.",
    "ingestion_mode": "import",
    "ingested_at": "2026-01-01",
    "notes": "All values EUR-equivalent converted from SEK (2022 avg: 10.90 SEK/EUR). Gross annual salary. Full-time employees."
